    "The feeder contains a mix of residential, commercial, and small industrial loads with time-varying characteristics.",
    "Transformer parameters are modeled with a resistance of R tr = 0.01 p.u., a reactance of X tr = 0.04 p.u., and a load-to-no-load ratio of T load /T no-load = 0.8/0.2.",
